{"tid":2182720,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"波羅的海三國擬制裁盧卡申科等30名白羅斯官員","createTime":"2020-08-31T13:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T12:59:55.000Z","uid":79563,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"357a45a04cee754acb5481941626b7cc86537045","tid":2182720,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:11:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547046-20200831.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547046-20200831.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=2%2FmELneL9Q%2Bp6j2sEUyr046aL69TDc1SPHZju%2B%2BXLiQ%3D&h=e7a16e88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1547046-20200831.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=63c39623\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1547046-20200831.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n立陶宛總統瑙塞達表示，將聯同另外兩個波羅的海國家拉脫維亞及愛沙尼亞，制裁白俄羅斯總統盧卡申科等30名白俄官員，指他們涉嫌操縱總統選舉及武力鎮壓示威者。<br />\n<br />\n瑙塞達表示，三國之前已表明，白俄羅斯政府與社會之間需要和平對話，達成協議，但看不到白俄當局有為此作準備。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，歐盟亦正草擬類似的制裁名單，但盧卡申科日前威脅會報復，切斷歐洲與俄羅斯之間途經白俄的運輸路線。白俄羅斯是歐洲貨物運往俄羅斯的主要陸上路線，亦鋪有用於將俄羅斯石油運往歐洲的管道。<br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯克里姆林宮表示，白俄局勢受控，看不到需要派警力支持盧卡申科。"},{"pid":"3031f8d3bb8a96f5534f59d69e12cd1973286816","tid":2182720,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:16:40.000Z","msg":"歐盟打鳩佢未"},{"pid":"e26d486c7ecc68fd9236840992c8ec4d754e20ba","tid":2182720,"uid":47492,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"三小都勇過德狗"},{"pid":"b02810597a8844d4d9ef8fed5cf8b0aa23748369","tid":2182720,"uid":34065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-31T13:30:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f4d45e3f0375114b46733b63c66ad15a077e971","tid":2182720,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26d486c7ecc68fd9236840992c8ec4d754e2